=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in the=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30923484.257437/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2=
