G1fdGVybT0yMzAzMjImdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23c=
B756831a8" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank"=
 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;">  wealth management business in Asia</a>=C2=A0is an impo=
rtant part of its success, imposing losses on those clients has some proble=
ms.)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">By the way, it=E2=80=99s also bad if AT1s are =
held in margin accounts at banks! You don=E2=80=99t want banks to have much=
 exposure to other banks=E2=80=99 AT1s, because then zeroing one bank=E2=80=
=99s AT1 causes losses at other banks and can create contagion.</p>
